charges.charge_description: On or about January 26, 2013, in Jackson County, in the Western District of Missouri, and elsewhere, the defendant DANIEL MCCUTCHEN, defendant herein, having been convicted of a crime punishable by imprisonment for a term exceeding one year, did knowingly possess, in and affecting interstate commerce, a firearm, to wit: a Taurus, .45 caliber handgun, Model PT145, Serial Number NAW48726, contrary to the provisions of Title 18, United States Code, Sections 922(g)(1) and 924(a)(2).
